{"data":[{"date":"08:40 23/06","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ebb h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t nh\u00e0 vua","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00ec l\u1ee3m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua HAGL nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 u\u1ec3 o\u1ea3i trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</h2><h2>S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1eebng &lsquo;h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t&rsquo; H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i&hellip;</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi\u1ebfn CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1edfi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eadm. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf m\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u1eabn l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u1edf ngay l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ebb h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t nh\u00e0 vua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ebb h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t nh\u00e0 vua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Du-am-HAGL-3-2-Sai-Gon-FC-Dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>S\u00e0i G\u00f2n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh qu\u1eadt c\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eb1ng 11 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfm ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch t\u1edbi 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC v\u00e0 t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ee9ng minh s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi &lsquo;h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p&rsquo; th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam trong c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd b\u1edfi t\u00ednh minh b\u1ea1ch, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t hay d\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh qua nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>&hellip; nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Pleiku c\u1ee7a HAGL v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u 22/6. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em s\u1ebd &lsquo;an to\u00e0n&rsquo; nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu thua, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p HAGL, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC r\u1ea5t khao kh\u00e1t c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t HAGL s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ra v\u1ec1 tay tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL\" title=\"HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/SG-GL6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><i>D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">90 ph\u00fat t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n thua t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao HAGL. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 nh\u1eadn ra CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1ed1n v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua chu\u1ed7i 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn hay, tr\u1eadn d\u1edf, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV T\u00e0i Em s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ec7n minh cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n tinh th\u1ea7n Iceland n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap HLV T\u00e0i Em c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1eebng cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 tham kh\u1ea3o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Iceland tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u1edb tr\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n sinh n\u0103m 1982 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c HAGL, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u1ea7n qu\u00ean chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch phi th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t v\u00e0 d\u1ed3n s\u1ee9c cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. Khi m\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh s\u1ebd tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng sau 12 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 T\u00e0i Em s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Vinh g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp su\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 SLNA. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01a1 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a t\u1edbi c\u0169ng \u0111ang hi\u1ec7n ra r\u00f5 n\u00e9t h\u01a1n v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/BXH-sau-vong-15-V-League.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>BXH V-League 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"479","checkdouble":"189318"},{"date":"07:29 23/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia (19h00 ng\u00e0y 23/6): V\u00e9 s\u1edbm cho b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/Bi-vs-Tunisia.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018: M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong t\u1ea7m tay th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Roberto Martinez \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft tranh ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ec9: Th\u1eafng to m\u00e0 v\u1eabn lo</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ec9 ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 ra, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 v\u00e0 ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng ch\u1ec9 thua ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Roberto Martinez th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh Panama ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn c\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00f4 danh v\u00e0 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec World Cup 2018, B\u1ec9 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 nh\u1edd t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Dries Mertens \u0111\u1ec3 khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia 19h00 ng\u00e0y 236 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia 19h00 ng\u00e0y 236 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Nhan-dinh-Bi-vs-Tunisia-19h00-ngay-236-bang-G-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c B\u1ec9 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn do v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0nh, \u0111\u1eb1ng n\u00e0y h\u1ecd c\u00f2n b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ebfn ba ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 k\u00e9o theo, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng suy gi\u1ea3m lu\u00f4n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1ed1n ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng s\u1ef1 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00fa vu\u1ed1t b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Mertens, ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc c\u00e1i k\u1ebft t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Martinez. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea5y th\u00ec nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, bao g\u1ed3m b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kevin De Bruyne v\u00e0 Eden Hazard, b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 thay v\u00ec duy tr\u00ec l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i pressing c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafn, h\u1ecd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i cho m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb Panama h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i, v\u1edbi 7 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Man Utd d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-30-panama-khi-moi-loi-khen-di-kem-voi-mot-chu-nhung-421-188888.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/0.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-30-panama-khi-moi-loi-khen-di-kem-voi-mot-chu-nhung-421-188888.html\">B\u1ec9&hellip; v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Panama: Khi m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi khen \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ch\u1eef &ldquo;nh\u01b0ng&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 3-0 Panama l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec l\u01b0\u1ee3t ra qu\u00e2n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i c\u00e1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u1ea5t an \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ec1 d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf v\u1eabn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t cho l\u00fac n\u00e0y, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi World Cup 2018 \u0111ang l\u00e0 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt c\u00fa s\u1ed1c kh\u00f3 tin t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Lukaku c\u0169ng c\u1edfi tr\u00f3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd cho ch\u00ednh anh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1ng nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 s\u0103n b\u00e0n cho n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd mang th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua Ph\u00e1 L\u01b0\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tunisia: Ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tunisia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ea9n s\u1ed1 th\u00fa v\u1ecb \u1edf World Cup 2018, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng h\u1ea1ng cao nh\u1ea5t FIFA (14). T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i s\u00edt sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0110\u1ea1i B\u00e0ng v\u00f9ng Carthage \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn Anh m\u01b0\u1edbt m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i h\u1ed9t trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 thua 1-2 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a Tunisia c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecd v\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3 ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd do Harry Kane, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia (19h00 ng\u00e0y 236) V\u00e9 s\u1edbm cho b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia (19h00 ng\u00e0y 236) V\u00e9 s\u1edbm cho b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Nhan-dinh-Bi-vs-Tunisia-(19h00-ngay-236)-Ve-som-cho-bay-Quy-Do-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, Anh qu\u00e1 phung ph\u00ed nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00fang h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Tunisia \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Nabil Maaloul ch\u1ec9 s\u00e2u \u0111\u1eadm trong n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai khi t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng pressing \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1edbp. Ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ecbu tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 may m\u1eafn tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Tam S\u01b0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00ec c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1edfi Anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu Harry Kane, trung phong xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec Tunisia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t n\u1ebfu ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Bi vs Tunisia\" title=\"Preview B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Bi-vs-Tunisia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0110\u1ea1i B\u00e0ng v\u00f9ng Carthage h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eeb h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng mong manh cho h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb b\u1ecf l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1eed tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tunisia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i, trong khi B\u1ec9 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng hoan ngh\u00eanh ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110\u1ea1i B\u00e0ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 ti\u1ebfp theo v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc Phi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ec9 (3-4-2-1):&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>1. Courtois;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>2. Alderweireld &ndash; 20. Boyata &ndash; 5. Vertonghen;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>15. Meunier &ndash; 7. De Bruyne &ndash; 6. Witsel &ndash; 11. Carrasco;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>14. Mertens &ndash; 10. Hazard;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>9. Lukaku<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tunisia (4-1-4-1):&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>1. Mustapha; 1<o:p></o:p>1. Bronn &ndash; 4. Meriah &ndash; 2. Youssef &ndash; 12. Maaloul;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>17. Skhiri;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>8. Youssef &ndash; 13. Sassi &ndash; 9. Badri &ndash; 23. Sliti;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>10. Khazri</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia: 2-0\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Bi vs Panama\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 vs Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Bi-vs-Panama-(3-4-2-1-vs-4-1-4-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"478","checkdouble":"189324"},{"date":"08:37 23/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico (22h ng\u00e0y 23/6): \"Chi\u1ebfn binh Teageuk\" v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/nhan-dinh-han-quoc-vs-mexico-22h-ngay-236-chien-binh-teageuk-ve-nuoc-som.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mexico \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sau kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc M\u0129 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out ngay sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn h\u00f4m nay.</h2><h2>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu \u1edbt</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i World Cup. Sau khi th\u00fac th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Mexico kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0i to\u00e1n \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Kh\u00e2u ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c &ldquo;chi\u1ebfn binh Taegeuk&rdquo; \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. V\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 12 trong 13 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico (22h ng\u00e0y 236) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico (22h ng\u00e0y 236) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Han-quoc-vs-mexico.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n trong 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng cho H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i trong 3 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n \u1edf World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, vi\u1ec7c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc. HLV Uli Stielike \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c1. HLV Shin Tae-yong l\u00ean thay nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-0. May m\u1eafn cho H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111\u1ebfn Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Son Heung-min l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup ph\u1ea3i e d\u00e8.</div>\r\n<h2>Mexico \u0111ang tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang g\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u00e1y th\u00ec Mexico l\u1ea1i tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>, El Tri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c virus c\u00fam \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f9ng ph\u00e1t \u1edf tr\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mexico \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0y binh b\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. H\u1ecd lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd thay v\u00ec co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Mexico \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 World Cup v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hirving Lozano la hien tuong moi cua bong da Mexico.\" title=\"Hirving Lozano l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Mexico.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/giai-ma-hirving-lozano-el-chucky-ke-thich-gieo-rac-noi-so-hai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mexico c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft World Cup 2018 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t La-tinh trong m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u, Mexico gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng. El Tri \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 hi\u1ec7u h\u00f3a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Mexico \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc M\u0129 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t gi\u1eefa kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ef1u binh d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Guardado, Vela, Chicharito hay Ochoa v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a El Tri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang nh\u01b0 Salcedo, Gallardo v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Lozano. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c, sao tr\u1ebb Lozano \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o \u0111ang gi\u00fap anh l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG H\u00e0 Lan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, vi\u1ec7c Mexico gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn x\u1ea3y ra, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o th\u1ebf ch\u00e2n t\u01b0\u1eddng. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0o c\u0169ng d\u1edf t\u1ec7 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico:</strong><br>\r\n- L\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1998, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc M\u0129 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 3-1<br>\r\n- H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 12 trong 13 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi trong 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp<br>\r\n- H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng trong 7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup, thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp<br>\r\n- Mexico gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup khi g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c1<br>\r\n- Mexico m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 thua 2 trong 18 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup<br>\r\n- Mexico ch\u01b0a th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2002<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Han Quoc vs Mexico\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Han-Quoc-vs-Mexico-(4-3-3-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1: 0-2</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/son-heungmin-tu-hy-vong-tro-thanh-that-vong-421-188946.html\">Son Heung-min: T\u1eeb hy v\u1ecdng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-khien-bong-da-han-quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-world-cup-2018-421-188894.html\">3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"477","checkdouble":"189327"},{"date":"08:48 23/06","title":"\u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (01h00 ng\u00e0y 24/6): Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/23/duc-vs-thuy-dien-01h00-ngay-246-them-mot-bat-ngo.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i, Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c phong \u0111\u1ed9. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2>\u0110KV\u0110 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m khi b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 0-1, nh\u01b0ng \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 n\u00e9t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">So v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i Confed Cup c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Die Mannschaft s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n em. Joachim Low, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft b\u00e0i v\u1edf, v\u00e0 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc to\u00e0n t\u1eadp \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, trong khi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c h\u1edf ra nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3. Theo <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-mexico-mats-hummels-ly-giai-viec-hang-thu-dt-duc-choi-te-465-188763.html\" target=\"_blank\">trung v\u1ec7 Hummels l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico</span>, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00f2n 1-2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u00ec <strong>&ldquo;ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 b\u1eb1ng m\u1eaft \u00e0?&rdquo;</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/DKVD-Duc-thua-soc-ngay-ra-quan-Low-da-thuc-su-het-bai-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng \u01b0ng \u00fd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Thomas Muller. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Bayern \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1eaft Joshua Kimmich ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh c\u1ea3 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb lao h\u1eb3n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ec3 tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, b\u1edfi Muller kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. H\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3, c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Kimmich \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Joachim Low c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. H\u1ecd qu\u00e1 n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 m\u00e0 tung t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi r\u00fat lu\u00f4n Khedira ra ngo\u00e0i. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, Mexico kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t, v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa (ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n duy nh\u1ea5t Kroos \u0111\u00e1 trung t\u00e2m).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Joachim Low ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0110KV\u0110 ti\u1ebfp theo b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Low\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/duc3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Low c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Janne Andersson \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u tay tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u1eafm ch\u00fat l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng F. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 Mexico, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, khi h\u1ecd&hellip; ch\u1eb3ng h\u01a1n g\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ibrahimovic, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. N\u00ean nh\u1edb, HLV Andersson to\u00e0n quy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ibra, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u00ec mu\u1ed1n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, nh\u01b0ng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Mexico l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft tay nhau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo (trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p El Tri h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c). \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ra chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/3-yeu-to-khien-DT-Han-Quoc-khong-the-tao-dia-chan-tai-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u tay t\u1ea1i World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Die Mannschaft ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian qu\u00e1 d\u00e0i \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng. \u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m, m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a Joachim Low, v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ed7 v\u00e0i nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng Kimmich v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd lao l\u00ean b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nguy hi\u1ec3m ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Janne Andersson s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u0169i c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Emil Forsberg &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Bundesliga. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, anh hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a Kimmich, v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd khai th\u00e1c tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Hirving Lozano c\u1ee7a Mexico \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u m\u00e0 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f4i khi khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd c\u00e0ng th\u00eam b\u1ed1i r\u1ed1i. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Preview \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/duc-vs-thuy-dien-01h00-ngay-246-them-mot-bat-ngo.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- \u0110\u1ee9c thua Mexico m\u1edbi l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2 trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup, sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m 1982. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, tin t\u00edch c\u1ef1c l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 11 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 40 n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1o ra 16 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 2 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (4-4, 5-3).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- \u0110\u1ee9c ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn trong 4 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Muller ghi 10 b\u00e0n sau 14 c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 5 l\u1ea7n trong 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eebng ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n 2 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3 (Italia 1950 v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c 1958).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng sau 402 ph\u00fat li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Joachim Low c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf r\u01a1i Ozil tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Marcos Reus \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Hummels c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf c\u1ed5, trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sami Khedira c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i, sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Ilkay Gundogan, ho\u1eb7c Leon Goretzka.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean ph\u00eda Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man United &ndash; Victor Lindelof \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1ecfi \u1ed1m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 5\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Nhan-dinh-Duc-vs-Thuy-Dien-bang-F-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: 1-1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 6\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/F.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-ay-la-zlatan-nhung-chung-ta-la-thuy-dien-421-188871.html\">Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 Zlatan, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-thuy-dien-10-han-quoc-bang-f-world-cup-2018-461-188852.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lozano-ghi-ban-ha-guc-duc-mot-cdv-mexico-bat-ngo-lay-duoc-vo-421-188930.html\">Lozano ghi b\u00e0n h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110\u1ee9c, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Mexico b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ee3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-world-cup-2018-h1-461-188750.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/duc-thua-soc-mexico-ngay-ra-quan-khong-som-canh-tinh-loi-nguyen-nha-dkvd-se-linh-ung-421-188770.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c thua s\u1ed1c Mexico: Kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh, l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 s\u1ebd linh \u1ee9ng!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"476","checkdouble":"189328"},{"date":"02:28 23/06","title":"HLV Iceland v\u1eabn m\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 \u1edf World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-iceland-van-mo-dieu-than-ky-o-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Hallgrimsson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 51 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u khi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Iceland ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018, Iceland \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c khi c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Argentina 1-1. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Vi\u1ec7c Argentina thua Croatia 0-3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Iceland th\u1eafp s\u00e1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hallgrimsson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Hallgrimsson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/HLV-Hallgrimsson-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Nigeria-vs-Iceland-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Iceland \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nigeria 0-2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 n\u1ebfu Iceland \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Hallgrimsson \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t khi d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 1.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nSang hi\u1ec7p 2 khi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng Iceland kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng so v\u1edbi Nigeria, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i chung cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-cua-nigeria-truoc-iceland-421-189312.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Nigeria vs Iceland</span> vinh danh Musa, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n cho \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u201d. V\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Iceland tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Hallgrimsson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 51 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u khi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Heimir Hallgrimsson cung la mot nha si.\" title=\"HLV Heimir Hallgrimsson c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nha s\u0129.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Heimir-Hallgrimsson.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Heimir Hallgrimsson tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Iceland s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi Iceland \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong hi\u1ec7p 1 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t trong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n gi\u00fap Nigeria gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Iceland l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1eb9p, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u khi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Croatia v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cIceland \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 \u1edf Euro 2016 khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c \u1edf World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)<br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"475","checkdouble":"189313"},{"date":"02:55 23/06","title":"HLV Nigeria: \"H\u00e3y mang Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/hlv-nigeria-hay-mang-argentina-den-day.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland, HLV 64 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u201d s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nigeria xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Iceland</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Nigeria bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Gernot-Rohr-noi-ve-tran-Nigeria-vs-Iceland-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nigeria \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Iceland v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nD\u00f9 c\u00f3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng song \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u201d kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, trong c\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p 1 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, khung th\u00e0nh Nigeria th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-nigeria-20-iceland-421-189309.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Nigeria vs Iceland</span> cho th\u1ea5y trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 5 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, 3 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh. N\u1ebfu Finnbogason v\u00e0 Sigurdsson ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Iceland \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nSang hi\u1ec7p 2, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c Nigeria d\u1ea7n l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Ph\u00fat 49, Musa m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n, t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 75 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t pha solo n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i Iceland \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0, Nigeria \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng D, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1eabn c\u00f2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Nigeria th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Argentina</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland, HLV 64 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u201d s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gernot Rohr phat bieu ve tran Nigeria vs Iceland\" title=\"Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/hlv-nigeria-hay-mang-argentina-den-day.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft, ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. Nigeria \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Iceland\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Argentina \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Nigeria c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"474","checkdouble":"189314"},{"date":"03:04 23/06","title":"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/clip-ban-thang-serbia-vs-thuy-si.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Xherdan Shaqiri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Stoke \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nSau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Serbia v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E. Tuy nhi\u00ean tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh khi Aleksandar Mitrovic m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xherdan Shaqiri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xherdan Shaqiri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Xherdan-Shaqiri-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Serbia-vs-Thuy-Sy-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia 2-1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nTh\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ph\u00fat 52, Granit Xhaka th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa n\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e1c t\u1ea7m xa g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nT\u1edbi ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Xherdan Shaqiri t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 cho Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-serbia-vs-thuy-si-421-189311.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 </span>gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f2a Costa Rica, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Shaqiri \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xherdan Shaqiri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Stoke \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaqiri phat bieu ve tran Serbia vs Thuy Sy\" title=\"Shaqiri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/giup-thuy-sy-gianh-3-diem-truoc-serbia-shaqiri-noi-gi.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Shaqiri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cTh\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 l\u00e0 t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 quen v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. B\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1ecb nao n\u00fang khi Serbia c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cC\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ki\u00ean \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Serbia l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p cho nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"473","checkdouble":"189315"},{"date":"03:32 23/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-serbia-12-thuy-si.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng E VCK World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Serbia (v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp) so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 ch\u1ec9 thua 1 trong 24 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng 17, h\u00f2a 6.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c sau khi b\u1ecb m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Xhaka-ghi-ban-cho-Thuy-Si.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Xhaka \u0103n m\u1eebng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n- Granit Xhaka \u0111\u00e3 ghi 10 b\u00e0n cho Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 bao g\u1ed3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia th\u00ec 5 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Aleksandar Mitrovic \u0111\u00e3 ghi 18 b\u00e0n sau 26 tr\u1eadn cho CLB v\u00e0 \u0110TQG trong n\u0103m 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Mitrovic \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 15 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 15 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t cho Serbia (13 b\u00e0n, 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Serbia \u0111\u00e3 thua trong c\u1ea3 6 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup sau khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n trong 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i World Cup, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 3 b\u00e0n trong 10 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Stephan Lichtsteiner \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 cho Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 t\u1ea1i World Cup, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Josef Hugi (6) \u0111\u00e3 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u01a1n Xherdan Shaqiri (4 b\u00e0n, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Robert Ballamann v\u00e0 Andre Abegglen).<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-serbia-vs-thuy-si-461-189315.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/clip-ban-thang-serbia-vs-thuy-si.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-serbia-vs-thuy-si-461-189315.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018)</span><br />\r\n<span>B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e9p v\u1ebf trong hi\u1ec7p 1, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-serbia-vs-thuy-si-463-189293.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/ket-qua-serbia-vs-thuy-si.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-serbia-vs-thuy-si-463-189293.html\">Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (KT): Th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c, Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8</span><br />\r\n<span>B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e9p v\u1ebf trong hi\u1ec7p 1, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br />\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"472","checkdouble":"189316"},{"date":"03:47 23/06","title":"4 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/3-yeu-to-quyet-dinh-tran-dau-brazil-20-costa-rica.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Brazil cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Costa Rica thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngoan c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 4 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica m\u1edbi ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, c\u00e1c v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas. Ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Brazil m\u1edbi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Coutinho \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf ra chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Selecao tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m. N\u00f3 c\u0169ng ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo g\u1eb7p Serbia v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n cao nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 4 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>1. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Douglas Costa<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, Douglas Costa kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, anh ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1ch s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u1ea1i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng mang t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho Selecao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian Willian thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng thi tri\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd n\u00e0o b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Ph\u1ea7n v\u00ec h\u1eadu v\u1ec7\u00a0Fagner kh\u00f4ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c l\u00ean tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Willian kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed3ng bi\u00ean, ph\u1ea7n v\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil nh\u1eadn ra ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 \u00edt chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng cho anh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/3-yeu-to-quyet-dinh-tran-dau-Brazil-2-0-Costa-Rica-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Douglas Costa ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p 2</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, Willian \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u2018ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh\u2019 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, bu\u1ed9c HLV Tite ph\u1ea3i tung Douglas Costa v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. V\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng k\u0129 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t tia ch\u1edbp, Costa \u0111\u00e3\u00a0li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u2018h\u00e0nh h\u1ea1\u2019 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 gia nua c\u1ee7a Costa Rica b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng pha b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, Costa c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Neymar ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa t\u00e2m l\u00fd r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho N10 v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh s\u1ebd c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. N\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Coutinho<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi \u0111\u00f3ng vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng cho Brazil \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Coutinho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi c\u00fa b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf ra chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a tinh th\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi m\u00e0 Brazil \u0111ang b\u1ecb Costa Rica c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a. Khi \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Brazil \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, v\u00ec h\u1ecd s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"4 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/4-yeu-to-quyet-dinh-tran-dau-Brazil-2-0-Costa-Rica-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Coutinho ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 cho Brazil</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t may \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ebf t\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec Coutinho l\u1ea1i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac. S\u1ef1 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng \u0111i xuy\u00ean qua hai ch\u00e2n Keylor Navas \u0111\u1ec3 ghim v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung M\u1ef9. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Coutinho \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Neymar<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn n\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ki\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 \u0110T Brazil l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd h\u1ebft v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u1eeba qua, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Anh b\u1ecb h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ebfn 10 l\u1ea7n, m\u1ed9t k\u1ec9 l\u1ee5c \u1edf World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Alan Shearer c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh b\u1ecb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tunisia l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1998. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Neymar g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 d\u1ea5y l\u00ean m\u1ed1i lo ng\u1ea1i anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Brazil v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 l\u00e0 ch\u1ed7 d\u1ef1a \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil thang Costa Rica 2-0 Neymar\" title=\"Brazil thang Costa Rica 2-0 Neymar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Brazil-thang-Costa-Rica-2-0-Neymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u00a0Neymar c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Costa Rica</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n, sang t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Costa Rica, Neymar kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u2018ch\u0103m s\u00f3c\u2019 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady n\u00ean phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, Costa Rica l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u00e8m ng\u01b0\u1eddi khu v\u1ef1c thay v\u00ec b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed 1 k\u00e8m 1. N\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Neymar c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea5t di\u1ec5n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh Costa Rica. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a anh khi\u1ebfn khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Costa Rica lu\u00f4n trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng. V\u00e0 sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1ecb b\u1ecf l\u1ee1, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Neymar c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, Neymar ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 1 trong 3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Selecao tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica. Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Brazil c\u1ee7a Neymar s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.\u00a0<br>\r\n<h2>4. T\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Tite<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00fat ra nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi \u0110T Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y HLV Tite \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. \u00d4ng b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Neymar \u0111\u00e1 l\u1ec7ch c\u00e1nh thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ea7m tr\u1ecbch tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Coutinho, v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 160 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ee7a Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edf b\u00f3ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o d\u00e0nh cho Neymar v\u00e0 Gabriel Jesus \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tite cua Brazil\" title=\"HLV Tite cua Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/10/hlv-tite-neymar-can-them-thoi-gian.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Tite n\u1eafm m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Brazil</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a HLV Tite c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng Douglas Costa trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Willian thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t. Costa sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, HLV Tite c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Mexico n\u00ean y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1eafc, tr\u00e1nh m\u1eafc b\u1eaby ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Miranda c\u00f9ng Thiago Silva ch\u01a1i d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ec3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u00e1p s\u00e1t khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1edd th\u1ebf m\u00e0 Brazil c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. N\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Brazil. N\u1ebfu Tite v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 minh m\u1eabn trong vi\u1ec7c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a\u00a0Selecao, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfn xa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-costa-rica-461-189287.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/1_10.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-costa-rica-461-189287.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nT\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra bi\u1ebft bao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n song ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian th\u00eam gi\u1edd, Selecao m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Coutinho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi khai th\u00f4ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-20-costa-rica-421-189299.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/Philippe-Coutinho-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Brazil-vs-Costa-Rica-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-20-costa-rica-421-189299.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica</span><br>\r\nBrazil \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Costa Rica v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Costa Rica...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sut-tung-luoi-costa-rica-neymar-lot-vao-top-3-chan-sut-vi-dai-nhat-brazil-421-189297.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/sut-tung-luoi-costa-rica-neymar-lot-vao-top-3-chan-sut-vi-dai-nhat-brazil.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sut-tung-luoi-costa-rica-neymar-lot-vao-top-3-chan-sut-vi-dai-nhat-brazil-421-189297.html\">S\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Costa Rica, Neymar l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t Brazil</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Costa Rica, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil Romario \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf \u0110T...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"471","checkdouble":"189317"},{"date":"04:52 23/06","title":"Gi\u00fap Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia, Shaqiri n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/giup-thuy-sy-gianh-3-diem-truoc-serbia-shaqiri-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Xherdan Shaqiri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Stoke \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nSau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Serbia v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E. Tuy nhi\u00ean tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh khi Aleksandar Mitrovic m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xherdan Shaqiri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xherdan Shaqiri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Xherdan-Shaqiri-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Serbia-vs-Thuy-Sy-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia 2-1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nTh\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ph\u00fat 52, Granit Xhaka th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa n\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e1c t\u1ea7m xa g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nT\u1edbi ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Xherdan Shaqiri t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 cho Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-serbia-vs-thuy-si-421-189311.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 </span>gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f2a Costa Rica, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Shaqiri \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xherdan Shaqiri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Stoke \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaqiri phat bieu ve tran Serbia vs Thuy Sy\" title=\"Shaqiri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/giup-thuy-sy-gianh-3-diem-truoc-serbia-shaqiri-noi-gi.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Shaqiri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cTh\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 l\u00e0 t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 quen v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. B\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1ecb nao n\u00fang khi Serbia c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cC\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ki\u00ean \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Serbia l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p cho nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"470","checkdouble":"189319"},{"date":"05:08 23/06","title":"Thua Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, HLV Serbia tuy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Brazil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/thua-thuy-sy-hlv-serbia-tuyen-chien-voi-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Mladen Krstajic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 bu\u1ed9c HLV c\u1ee7a Serbia ph\u1ea3i tuy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Brazil \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1t khao gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m khi\u1ebfn Serbia ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nSerbia sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, h\u1ecd ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Aleksandar Mitrovic ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mladen Krstajic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mladen Krstajic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/HLV-Mladen-Krstajic-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Serbia-vs-Thuy-Sy-hinh-anh.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u00f9 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng Serbia l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y s\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3 Matic v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng. Vi\u1ec7c phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn Serbia ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNgay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 Xhaka \u0111\u00e3 tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn di\u1ec5n ra c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. Nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng Serbia s\u1ebd h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u1eb1m gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nT\u00ednh to\u00e1n sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a HLV Mladen Krstajic \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Serbia ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1. Vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn Serbia b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f2n ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nPh\u00fat 90, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh Xherdan Shaqiri d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tinh t\u1ebf qua h\u00e1ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Sommer gi\u00fap Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/giup-thuy-sy-gianh-3-diem-truoc-serbia-shaqiri-noi-gi-421-189319.html\" target=\"_blank\">Xherdan Shaqiri sau \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</span>, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Stoke \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Serbia tuy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Brazil</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Mladen Krstajic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 bu\u1ed9c HLV c\u1ee7a Serbia ph\u1ea3i tuy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Brazil \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Krstajic phat bieu ve tran Serbia vs Thuy Sy\" title=\"Krstajic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/thua-thuy-sy-hlv-serbia-tuyen-chien-voi-brazil.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Krstajic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng Serbia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. Serbia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn r\u1ee7i ro v\u00e0 b\u00e0n thua kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cTr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng khi b\u1ecb d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c. Serbia \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Brazil\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"469","checkdouble":"189320"},{"date":"04:38 23/06","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9: Tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi Xherdan Shaqiri","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/du-am-serbia-12-thuy-sy-tuyet-voi-xherdan-shaqiri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Xherdan Shaqiri ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, qua \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i in d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u1edf World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xherdan Shaqiri bay cao c\u00f9ng Th\u1ee5y s\u1ef9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Serbia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018, tham v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 b\u1ecb d\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh khi Aleksandar Mitrovic \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xherdan Shaqiri ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xherdan Shaqiri ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/sy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia 2-1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Vladimir Petkovic v\u1eabn ki\u00ean tr\u00ec theo \u0111u\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nXherdan Shaqiri ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u00ednh gi\u00fap Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia, HLV Vladimir Petkovic quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1, Shaqiri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Stoke c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Blerim Dzemaili v\u00e0 Steven Zuber l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 trung phong Haris Seferovic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y s\u1ef9 Shaqiri l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 chi chuy\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t n\u0103ng n\u1ed5, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a anh khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Serbia c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Aleksandar Kolarov \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 khi ph\u1ea3i theo k\u00e8m ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i, kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap anh chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Shaqiri.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn Kolarov th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111eo b\u00e1m ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xherdan Shaqiri choi noi bat trong chien thang cua Thuy Sy truoc Serbia\" title=\"Xherdan Shaqiri ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/sakiri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Xherdan Shaqiri ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nShaqiri \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9. Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 77 l\u1ea7n, th\u1ef1c&nbsp;hi\u1ec7n 46 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 89%.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Stoke c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi, anh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 4 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i v\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebfn v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 100%. Shaqiri l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 v\u1edbi 8 l\u1ea7n, chi\u1ebfm 45% t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Shaqiri g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ph\u00fat 52, t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Serbia ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng ra \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00fang t\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Xhaka, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ef1c c\u0103ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn khi m\u00e0 Serbia d\u1ed3n l\u00ean quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh b\u1eaby ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u00ednh l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang v\u00e0o ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Gavranovic th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Serbia ph\u00e1 h\u1ee5t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 th\u1ebf l\u00e0 Shaqiri ung dung \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba r\u1ed3i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ecm h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Serbia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXherdan Shaqiri ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y&nbsp;ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Stoke. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua s\u1ef1 truy c\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Yann Sommer b\u0103ng ra r\u1ea5t nhanh song Shaqiri v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng qua h\u00e1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 9 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG, quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia, Shaqiri x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaqiri phat bieu ve tran Serbia vs Thuy Sy\" title=\"Shaqiri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/giup-thuy-sy-gianh-3-diem-truoc-serbia-shaqiri-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Shaqiri ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u00e0o 100% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Stoke ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil. Ch\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 23 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng treo b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 Steven Zuber g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00ednh ra c\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u1edf World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil v\u00e0 Serbia \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Shaqiri, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y anh l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Vladimir Petkovic v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-serbia-vs-thuy-si-421-189311.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Serbia vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Petkovic d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Brazil \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Costa Rica, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Shaqiri v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t<br>\r\n</span></strong><span style=\"white-space:pre\"><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Serbia 1-2 Thuy Sy\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Thong-so-Serbia-vs-Thuy-Sy.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 1-2 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"468","checkdouble":"189321"},{"date":"04:59 23/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec khi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Iceland \u2018tan ch\u1ea3y\u2019 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u2018s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng Phi ch\u00e2u\u2019 Nigeria?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/dieu-gi-khien-hien-tuong-iceland-tan-chay-truoc-suc-nong-phi-chau-nigeria.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina, \u0110T Iceland \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Nigeria thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9. V\u1eady \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea3o b\u0103ng Iceland?</h2><h2>1. S\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng Volgograd\u00a0<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Hallgr\u00edmsson \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Volgograd \u0111ang t\u0103ng cao tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Iceland v\u00e0 Nigeria di\u1ec5n ra. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 trung b\u00ecnh ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi bu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0a l\u00ean t\u1edbi 30 \u0111\u1ed9 C s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1ed1n quanh n\u0103m s\u1ed1ng trong b\u0103ng gi\u00e1 t\u1ea1i Iceland. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nigeria, khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 sinh ra v\u00e0 l\u1edbn l\u00ean t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u Phi n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4 h\u1ea1n quanh n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Iceland th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Iceland th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/20180622T161030Z_1007201017_RC1311340000_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPNGAICE.JPG\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p><em>\"B\u0103ng\" Iceland tan nhanh v\u00ec s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga</em></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn Iceland v\u00e0 Nigeria v\u1eeba qua, s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Volgograd Arena \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1o h\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iceland. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y qua, bao g\u1ed3m vi\u1ec7c luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp gi\u1eefa tr\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 quen v\u1edbi c\u00e1i n\u00f3ng khu v\u1ef1c mi\u1ec1n Nam n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iceland v\u1eabn b\u1ecb ng\u1ee3p khi ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 trong hi\u1ec7p 2 khi Iceland c\u00e0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e0ng h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i trong khi c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn binh Nigeria c\u00e0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e0ng h\u0103ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng m\u00e3nh th\u00fa say m\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eb1ng hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. Nigeria kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, Anh hay Argentina<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 \u0110T Iceland thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i EURO 2016 hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u01a1 b\u1eafp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00e2u \u00c2u hay Nam M\u1ef9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00e2u Phi. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1c nhau khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Iceland.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Musa an mung cung dong doi Nigeria\" title=\"Musa an mung cung dong doi Nigeria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/nigeria-20-iceland-dai-bang-cuu-song-argentina-va-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u00a0S\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 v\u00f4 t\u1eadn c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nigeria gi\u00fap h\u1ecd khu\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh Iceland</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 Iceland phong t\u1ecfa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u b\u1edfi h\u1ecd d\u00f9ng s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng khi l\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c ra \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Nigeria th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Iceland ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ecbu thi\u1ec7t. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Iceland t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay ch\u1ec9 gi\u1ecfi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ecfi t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, nay l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 Nigeria \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tri\u1ec3n khai \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng. V\u00f4 h\u00ecnh trung vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea3o b\u0103ng b\u1ecb v\u00f4 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c Iceland c\u00f3 v\u1eady<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Iceland kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf cho th\u1ea5y l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc. V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh cao to v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iceland th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha treo b\u00f3ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9. Ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng pha b\u1eadt cao kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 B\u1eafc \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Nigeria v\u00e0o th\u1ebf b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 treo b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9, Iceland kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u201cc\u1eeda tr\u00ean\u201d khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 l\u00fang t\u00fang. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i, Iceland bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u2018\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0103n c\u1ea3, ng\u00e3 v\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng\u2019 b\u1edfi Iceland \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u1edf \u0111o\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Iceland choi tot hon song khong co duoc ban thang\" title=\"Iceland ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n song kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/icenad.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a Iceland khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Heimir Hallgr\u00edmsson ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. M\u1ea3i m\u00ea t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Iceland \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh \u0111\u00f2n \u2018h\u1ed3i m\u00e3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng\u2019 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u2018ch\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh Nigeria\u2019. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Nigeria t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng ch\u1edbp nho\u00e1ng. Victor Moses x\u00e9 gi\u00f3 lao \u0111i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, r\u1ed3i chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o \u0111\u00fang t\u1ea7m di chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Ahmed Musa. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Leicester sau m\u1ed9t nh\u1ecbp kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf b\u00f3ng g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 tung ra c\u00fa volley nh\u01b0 b\u00faa b\u1ed5 l\u00e0m b\u00f3 tay th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Hannes Halldorsson.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Nigeria \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa t\u00e2m l\u00fd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi kh\u00ed th\u1ebf h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c. Trong khi Iceland \u1edf th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua chung cu\u1ed9c 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, nh\u00ecn chung c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 \u00edt \u0111i v\u1edbi Iceland. \u1ede tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng Croatia m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 d\u1ec5 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea3o b\u0103ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-iceland-van-mo-dieu-than-ky-o-world-cup-2018-421-189313.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-iceland-van-mo-dieu-than-ky-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-iceland-van-mo-dieu-than-ky-o-world-cup-2018-421-189313.html\">HLV Iceland v\u1eabn m\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 \u1edf World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nHLV Hallgrimsson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 51 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u khi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-nigeria-hay-mang-argentina-den-day-421-189314.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/hlv-nigeria-hay-mang-argentina-den-day.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-nigeria-hay-mang-argentina-den-day-421-189314.html\">HLV Nigeria: H\u00e3y mang Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y</span><br>\r\nGernot Rohr n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland, HLV 64 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u201d s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-cua-nigeria-truoc-iceland-421-189312.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-cua-nigeria-truoc-iceland.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-cua-nigeria-truoc-iceland-421-189312.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Nigeria tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland</span><br>\r\nNigeria \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Iceland v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 qua \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D. C\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Iceland.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nigeria-vs-iceland-461-189306.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-nigeria-20-iceland.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nigeria-vs-iceland-461-189306.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nigeria 2-0 Iceland (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn qu\u00e1 hay, t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh x\u1ee9 B\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o. Musa l\u00e0 t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 c\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Nigeria...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"467","checkdouble":"189325"},{"date":"06:50 23/06","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (23/6/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/23/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2362018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>